  "title": "Carpenter #76430",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Carpentry</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Carpenter</strong></li><li>Working Location: North - Woodlands</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days / Monday – Saturday: 8.30am – 6pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Gross Salary Up to SGD 4500 (Basic up to $3000 + OT)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Read and understand blueprints and drawings to follow project requirements</li><li>Measure, cut, shape, and assemble wood and other materials as needed</li><li>Build and install items like doors, window frames, staircases, floors, walls, partitions, and furniture</li><li>Use hand tools and woodworking machines safely</li><li>Do repair and maintenance work when needed</li><li>Set up scaffolding and temporary structures for construction projects</li><li>Make sure all work meets safety and quality standards</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. 1 year of experience working as a carpenter, either in construction or furniture making</li><li>Able to use carpentry tools and equipment, including both manual and power tools</li><li>Can read and follow technical diagrams and measurements</li><li>Able to work in warm or humid environments as needed</li><li>Comfortable working alone or with a team</li><li>Willing to work outside standard hours, including nights, weekends, and public holidays when required</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76430 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
